Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:06.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:09.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:10.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't myself just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:13.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:16.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:19.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:21.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:24.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My memories didn't return,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but my desire to see Linda is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:50.70,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(286,293)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}In the Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro odoru tomerarenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:03.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naite waratte kimi to no kioku zutto wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hontou no jibun wa doko ni iru toka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Otona ni narutte taihen de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa wasurete mo ii kana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yoru ga matte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo hazumase aeru toki wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hashagi mawareba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutaetai omoi ni ima
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:38.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kizuite shimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kako to mirai osorete ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo no mama ja ugeokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tanoshimeba it's all right hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:58.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana koto zenbu wasurete kimi to issho ni odori akaseba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:05.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Motto suteki na jibun ni nareru sonna ki ga suru no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:12.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Owaranai Golden Time gyutto chikazuku kimi to no kyori wa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:19.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukazu hanarezu mawari michi demo taisetsu ni shitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:47.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still didn't clearly understand what had happened the previous night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:53.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew I was the Tada Banri that loved Linda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and that feeling still hadn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:00.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The photo's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know I put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I might really die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? It's still early!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... in distress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have a fever. Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:22.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai, you seriously, really are a super nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:30.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to have had the wrong idea about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:37.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were an over-the-top cosplayer from Kawaguchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,putting on a brave front so you wouldn't be taken lightly in the big city,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:46.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,until the harsh Tokyo life changed you and you forgot neighborly love for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not from Kawaguchi, and this isn't cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:54.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... was it Kaminakazato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Warabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought you were really nice, suddenly you're being cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:14.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to drag me around by the nose with your tsundere-ness and break my spirit so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:18.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Linda-senpai would be nicer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai, did you take out your rage on Tada Banri and beat him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The idiot ended up this way himself and came to me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm out of smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... wait, Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should really quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some stuff you might be able to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:25.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your fever came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai sent me this text.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.00,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(182,105)}NANA-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.00,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(182,177)}No subject
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.00,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(137,262)}Tada Banri's going to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:56.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It surprised me, so I called her back, and she told me to wait at her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:19.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Let's try this next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little weird, but no one's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can eat bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can take your medicine after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where did I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For taking care of me, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I told you the other day that\NI'd support you in any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I made you skip your lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just let my kind self take care of you, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The one she calls Banri... isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:27.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To her, Banri is the high school Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,who was in the same class and the same track and field club as her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... where's your burnable trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He took his medicine, and he's eaten a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai's nice, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:12.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If she hadn't helped me,\NI really would've been in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how she looks, she's actually very caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how many times she's saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I let Kouko-chan know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She is your beloved girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what will satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:49.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:55.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's certain is that...\NI want to be with Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being with Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:03.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...makes Kaga-san seem like someone I met in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the world with Linda is reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and Kaga-san is fading like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If the world with Kaga-san is reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to appear in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:27.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,she'll fade into the scenery that's all blurred together by this fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably coming here as fast as she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:36.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... But Kaga-san's still resting with a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:04.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone in your apartment with another woman, despite having a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the very definition of cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've said that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... but this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko-chan, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so reckless when I'm not watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, now that I'm here, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:39.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I, your girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:43.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,will restore you to perfect health!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who caught the bouquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yana-san, 2D-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get married next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to do a comedy routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:09.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it'd be funny if I said you were cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there's no way my Tada-kun would cheat on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, you totally love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:28.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That absolute confidence makes me stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:35.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The power of being loved runs through me and makes me feel even better,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and that in turn makes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You looked pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, cut that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You really scared me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So Nana-san is your neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's acquainted with Linda-senpai, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There are no secrets between lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't hiding anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:22.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As his girlfriend, I'm truly grateful to you for taking care of my Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:27.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're a frighteningly good liar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely different from what you were saying earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you were saying, "He's cheating, cheating, cheating!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Tada-kun is cheating!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"He must be cheating!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and making a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you dragged us along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Restrain me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"If it comes to it, restrain me by force!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand 3D girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,3D?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've abandoned the third dimension, so they call me 2D-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My real name's Sato Takaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't introduce myself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a second year in the Festival Club with Tada Banri and Kouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My first vertical relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:22.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, please forgive Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he's really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:28.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know he seems normal, but he's a compulsive liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Poor boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't even know what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:42.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't shut up about us coming, so we skipped class to-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...go along home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The door's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such a fuss in front of a sick person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but she...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:01.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think you were cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:14.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...another girl came to take care of you before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't deny that I may have been upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should feel more threatened by Nana-senpai than by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai's the first one who saved Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's Nana-senpai like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:31.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She really does look like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She does! That really is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys going anywhere over summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought about it much yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans, Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like traveling abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:59.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the money to go abroad, but I do want to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:04.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, it's just the Festival Club and visiting home to see friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're not from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's all go to the beach together!" or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be fun to rent a car and go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we should all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We could go somewhere close, like Shonan, or go all the way to Izu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should come with us, Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be boring if Kouko were the only girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll invite Nana-senpai, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:44.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai doesn't seem like the type who'd like the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:47.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We should invite Oka-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We made that promise the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you invite Miss Ultrasonic, we won't have enough seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we rent a big car, it won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Miss Ultrasonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo confessed to her and was rejected instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell her about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They left around noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They could still make their afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:51.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, you don't need to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten anything, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the bread Linda-senpai bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For barging in with everyone when you're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For not taking care of you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For making a fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get any rest, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:20.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a good girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't seem to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:37.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of junk like me isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:46.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought so today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:54.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,someone like Linda-senpai would be much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kaga-san, are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:11.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're not over your cold yet, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Honest, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a cold, I couldn't have come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:33.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a fever like this when you're living on your own makes you anxious, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your useless, piece-of-junk girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I have more love than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything I can.
